  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Here are the steps I identified and propose to do:\r\n\r\n  - apply CSS classes manually\r\n  - remove theme, themeable\r\n  - keep individual CSS files\r\n  - make the theme a separate package (allows updating the theme without having to update react-instantsearch)\r\n  - add necessary build step to allow\r\n    import theme from react-instantsearch-themes-algolia\r\n    insertCSS(theme)\r\n    npmcdn CSS file for ease of download/test/prototype\r\n  - update documentation to point to npmcdn CSS file, show\r\n  how to load it via npm too\r\n  - update our documentation site to load default theme",
    "created_at": "2016-11-30T09:14:18Z",
